reviewText: As with all great comedians, Bengt is an astute observer of the human condition.  Very fun stuff!!!

Bengt is hilarious!  I've seen him several times at WiseGuys in Salt Lake -- and am always on the floor laughing.  I own this DVD, and all 3 of his audio CDs and can say they are all worth every nickel spent.  Whether you're a Mormon or not -- you will laugh until it hurts.  His facial expressions crack me up... great stuff!
